{"tid":2183443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[政府新聞公報] 首席法官李國能: 司法獨立, 三權分立, 互相制衡","createTime":"2020-09-01T02:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T04:26:36.000Z","uid":14918,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bd93a1e0664d1c07ffe43a41e22a795f091eddfe","tid":2183443,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"終審法院首席法官出席午餐會的演辭全文<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n            <span class=\"red\">司法獨立</span> 維持法治<br />\n            憲法發展 迎接挑戰<br />\n<br />\n  在普通法制度中，司法獨立是最基本的特色；香港的普通法制度也是一樣。<span class=\"red\">司法獨立是權力分立概念的核心。權力分立就是行政、立法和司法三權分立，互相制衡。</span><span class=\"blue\">法院的作用是確保立法和行政機關在執行其職責時遵守基本法和法律。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200110/26/1026146.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200110%2F26%2F1026146.htm&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=874c483d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200110/26/1026146.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nWayback Machine: <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191027070923/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200110/26/1026146.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20191027070923%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200110%2F26%2F1026146.htm&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=52679f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20191027070923/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200110/26/1026146.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9e6b19862c99ae60be7ed25050d2a697874e1df0","tid":2183443,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fd137f11b376acaed118178c6b35efac42c33a","tid":2183443,"uid":48083,"like":